//|     SECTION 15: FORWARD LOOP — DASHBOARD DRAWING                 |
//|                                                                  |
//|  Purpose: Draw UI objects from TOP to BOTTOM.                    |
//|  Rule: Loop goes 0 → N (human reading order).                    |
//|        Use the Zero-Flicker Engine (Section 8).                  |
